data.description: Need one-level living? This 2 bed, 1 bath on a corner lot may be just the ticket! All living space is on the main floor and many updates throughout including windows, kitchen cabinets and appliances, water heater, and furnace. Detached garage offers room for your vehicle and extra storage/workshop area. Basement includes mechanicals, egress for expansion, and plenty of storage. Call today to make this one yours!
